description: Nortec Minerals Corp. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. The company explores for gold and lithium deposits. It holds interests in the Tammela project located in southwest Finland. The company was formerly known as Nortec Ventures Corp. and changed its name to Nortec Minerals Corp. in January 2010. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Michael  Malana C.M.A., CPA, CMA, CPA
